---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service | Beaufort Laundry Fairy">
  <div class="pt-24 pb-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary hover:text-primary-dark transition-colors mb-8 text-sm font-medium">
      <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
      Back to Home
    </a>
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-heading mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-lg text-body space-y-6">
      <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> April 2026</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-heading mt-8">Service Description</h2>
      <p>Beaufort Laundry Fairy provides wash, dry, and fold laundry services with optional pickup and delivery in Beaufort County, SC, including Beaufort, Port Royal, Ladies Island, and Bluffton (zip codes 29901-29907, 29909, 29910, 29935), including MCAS Beaufort base housing.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-heading mt-8">Pricing & Payment</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Laundry is weighed after pickup or drop-off and invoiced per pound</li>
        <li>A 10 lb minimum applies per order</li>
        <li>No payment is collected at the time of booking</li>
        <li>An invoice with a secure payment link is sent via text before washing begins</li>
        <li>We accept credit/debit cards and bank transfers</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-heading mt-8">Scheduling & Cancellations</h2>
      <p>You may reschedule or cancel a pickup at any time by texting or contacting us directly. We appreciate at least 12 hours notice when possible.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-heading mt-8">Care & Liability</h2>
      <p>We treat all garments with care using quality laundry products. While we take every precaution, Beaufort Laundry Fairy is not responsible for damage to items that are not suitable for standard machine washing and drying. Please remove any items requiring special care (dry clean only, hand wash only, etc.) before pickup.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-heading mt-8">Service Area</h2>
      <p>Free pickup and delivery is available within our service area in Beaufort County, SC (zip codes 29901-29907, 29909, 29910, 29935). Discounted pricing is available for customers who drop off and pick up their laundry.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-heading mt-8">Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about these terms? Contact us at <a href="mailto:beaufortlaundryfairy@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-dark">beaufortlaundryfairy@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
